ai-kv7.2:1.1_0: There are no things associated with them.
ai-kv7.2:1.3_0: Doesn’t there any one that is mixed with prevails and shelts cessation?
ai-kv7.2:1.5_0: Sometimes there are, some prevail over a single one, solitary calm, Nāgas, and Paṭācārā.
ai-kv7.2:1.6_0: “There are no things associated with them.”
ai-kv7.2:2.1_0: the feelings constituent group, the perception constituent group,
ai-kv7.2:2.3_0: Feelings are one substantial. Taking the aggregates he said,
ai-kv7.2:2.4_0: “Feeling is the aggregates of feeling and perception.”
ai-kv7.2:3.2_0: the consciousness constituent group that provides fuel for attachment.
ai-kv7.2:3.4_0: And five hundred feelings that occurred to him,
ai-kv7.2:3.5_0: “Feling is the aggregates of consciousness associated with consciousness.”
ai-kv7.2:4.8_0: “Consciousness is the aggregates associated with conditions.”
ai-kv7.2:5.1_0: just as when oil has passed the oil lamp (there), solid food has not been destroyed,
ai-kv7.2:5.2_0: In the same way, those things are unattached, and transcended.
ai-kv7.2:5.3_0: And you don’t keep on doing it.
ai-kv7.2:5.4_0: The story at the associated states is finished.
